Richard A. Gottscho 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President, Global Products at LAM RESEARCH CORP, Richard A. Gottscho  made $4,617,676 in total compensation.  Of this total $545,296 was received as a salary, $781,174 was received as a bonus, $606,262 was received in stock options, $2,675,862 was awarded as stock and $9,082 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


