Biography of Richard Gottscho
                Last update: May 25, 2017            







Career

                                                                                Richard Gottscho graduated from The Pennsylvania State University and from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.                                                                                Richard was Head, Electronics Packaging Department for AT&T Bell Laboratory.                                                                                 Richard Gottscho joined Lam Research in 1996. Richard served as Group Vice President and General Manager, Etch Businesses at Lam Research.                                                

